name: Lena Schulze
tagline: Exploring the wiring of your brain
body: ### Geek + Engineer + Neuroscientist Lena spends most of her time doing research as a Phd student in the area of neural computation and machine learning at the [Okinawa Institute of Science and Technology (OIST)](http://www.oist.jp/), at the lab of [Kenji Doya](https://groups.oist.jp/ncu). In her spare time she develops iOS games in swift, paints, travels Asia, drinks a lot of coffee and cuddles with her cat Pankeki.
